summary: AN ORDINANCE approving and confirming the plat of "Village Homes at Othello Station Unit Lot Subdivision" a replat of Lots 7-27, Block 20 of Holly Park Subdivision No. 2 and Lot 1, Block 11 of NewHolly Townhomes Div. 2 being a portion of the SW 1/4 of the NW 1/4 of Section 27, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., in King County, Washington.
